<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Didattica GALILEI</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,400&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@300;400;600&display=swap');
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;background:#1a1a1e;color:#fff;min-height:100vh}
.hero{text-align:center;padding:80px 32px 48px;position:relative}
.hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg,transparent,transparent 40px,rgba(255,255,255,0.01) 40px,rgba(255,255,255,0.01) 41px)}
.eyebrow{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.28);margin-bottom:16px;font-weight:600}
h1{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,56px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:10px}
h1 em{color:#d4956a;font-style:italic}
.sub{font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);font-weight:300}
.section{max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;padding:48px 32px 0}
@media(max-width:600px){.section{padding:32px 16px 0}}
.sec-label{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:18px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.sec-label::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1)}
.sec-label.ph{color:#e07a5a}
.sec-label.ma{color:#74c99a}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-bottom:48px}
.card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:7px;padding:22px 22px 54px;text-decoration:none;color:#fff;display:block;transition:transform 0.18s,background 0.18s,border-color 0.18s;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.22)}
.card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:3px;height:100%}
.c1::before{background:#e07a5a}
.c2::before{background:#e0a05a}
.c3::before{background:#e0ca5a}
.c4::before{background:#74c99a}
.c5::before{background:#5ac9c9}
.c6::before{background:#7a9ae0}
.c7::before{background:#c97ab4}
.c8::before{background:#c9947a}
.num{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.28);margin-bottom:8px}
.card h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;line-height:1.25}
.card p{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);line-height:1.6;font-weight:300}
.tags{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap;position:absolute;bottom:14px;left:22px;right:36px}
.tag{font-size:9px;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:2px;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45)}
.arrow{position:absolute;bottom:16px;right:18px;font-size:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);transition:color 0.18s,transform 0.18s}
.card:hover .arrow{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);transform:translateX(3px)}
.card.soon{opacity:0.35;pointer-events:none}
.card.soon::after{content:'presto';position:absolute;top:12px;right:12px;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.28);padding:2px 7px;border-radius:2px;font-weight:600}
footer{text-align:center;font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);padding:32px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:16px}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="eyebrow">Didattica Pierri</div>
  <h1>Dispense<br><em>Interattive</em></h1>
  <p class="sub">Fisica e Matematica con simulatori interattivi</p>
</div>

<div class="section">

  <div class="sec-label ph">⚡ Fisica II — Elettrostatica</div>
  <div class="grid">

    <a class="card c1" href="simulatore_campo_elettrico.html">
      <div class="num">Fisica 01</div>
      <h2>Il Campo Elettrico</h2>
      <p>Linee di campo di fino a 4 cariche. Simulatore grafico e calcolatore numerico con unità reali (µC, nC, m, cm).</p>
      <div class="tags"><span class="tag">Simulatore 2D</span><span class="tag">Calcolatore E</span></div>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
    </a>

    <a class="card c2" href="dispensa_potenziale_completa.html">
      <div class="num">Fisica 02</div>
      <h2>Il Potenziale Elettrico</h2>
      <p>Equipotenziali 2D e superficie 3D di V(x,y) per fino a 4 cariche. Vista ruotabile.</p>
      <div class="tags"><span class="tag">2D + 3D</span><span class="tag">Equipotenziali</span></div>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
    </a>

    <a class="card c3" href="dispensa_distribuzioni.html">
      <div class="num">Fisica 03</div>
      <h2>Distribuzioni di Carica</h2>
      <p>Campo di piano, retta, sfera e conduttore irregolare. Mappa |E| e effetto punta.</p>
      <div class="tags"><span class="tag">4 simulatori</span><span class="tag">Effetto punta</span></div>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
    </a>

  </div>

  <div class="sec-label ma">∫ Matematica</div>
  <div class="grid">

    <a class="card c4" href="matematica/probabilita.html">
      <div class="num">Mat 01</div>
      <h2>Probabilità</h2>
      <p>Calcolo combinatorio, probabilità classica, eventi dipendenti, Bayes. Simulatori con moneta, dado e carte.</p>
      <div class="tags"><span class="tag">Simulatori</span><span class="tag">Combinatorio · Bayes</span></div>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
    </a>

    <a class="card c5" href="tre_perpendicolari.html">
      <div class="num">Mat 02</div>
      <h2>Tre Perpendicolari</h2>
      <p>Visualizzatore 3D del teorema e simulatore di piramide triangolare e quadrangolare con altezze delle facce.</p>
      <div class="tags"><span class="tag">3D interattivo</span><span class="tag">Piramide</span></div>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
    </a>

    <a class="card c6" href="geometria_spazio.html">
      <div class="num">Mat 03</div>
      <h2>Geometria dello Spazio</h2>
      <p>Piani, rette e vettori nello spazio. Equazioni cartesiane, forme parametriche, prodotto vettore. 5 simulatori 3D.</p>
      <div class="tags"><span class="tag">5 simulatori</span><span class="tag">3D interattivo</span></div>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
    </a>

    <a class="card c7 soon" href="#">
      <div class="num">Mat 04</div>
      <h2>Geometria Analitica</h2>
      <p>Coniche, curve parametriche e luoghi geometrici con visualizzazione interattiva.</p>
      <div class="tags"><span class="tag">Simulatori</span></div>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
    </a>

    <a class="card c8 soon" href="#">
      <div class="num">Mat 05</div>
      <h2>Numeri Complessi</h2>
      <p>Piano di Argand, operazioni, forme esponenziali e trasformazioni conformi.</p>
      <div class="tags"><span class="tag">Simulatori</span></div>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
    </a>

  </div>
</div>

<footer>Didattica Pierri · Fisica &amp; Matematica · Materiali interattivi</footer>
</body>
</html>
